volumeInfo.subtitle: An Entrepreneurial Approach
volumeInfo.description: For courses in Small Business Management. This practical, applied text focuses on business planning and the day-to-day issues of running a small business. This text stands out from others through its extensive integration of developing a business plan, and specifically through its integration of Business Plan Pro software (the most popular commercial software package used for business plan development).
volumeInfo.title: Effective Small Business Management
